Program: The Forum
Title: 28/06/2009: Part 1
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p003jbs8
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 29 Jun 2009
THE FORUM, the ideas programme with BRIDGET KENDALL. Kenyan environmentalist WANGARI MAATHAI on the link between culture and environmental degradation. American geneticist JANE PETERSON on the bacteria living within us. Former Yugoslav novelist DUBRAVKA UGRESIC on the power of old ladies.